    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Using this advanced Shoton technique, the user is encased in a prism of crystal. While in this state, the user is treated as having Total Cover for 1 round. The prism itself has a hardness of 25, 20 hit points and a resistance to Earth and Water 15. At the beginning of the user's next turn, a finely sharpened beam of concentrated chakra is fired from the prism as a ray attack that deals 7d8 points of fire damage that can be halved with a successful reflex save.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Effect:</b> Ray (see text)</p>\n<p><b>Empower:</b> The user may spend an additional 2 points of chakra to increase the damage dealt by 1d8. For every two additional hit die added in this fashion, the DC of this technique increases by 1.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
